description: With a mission to serve food that fuels New Havenites with nutrients as opposed to a plethora of processed ingredients, Food Extrovert offers an eclectic selection of local, healthy, and delicious cuisine. The best flavors of the world are used to craft their menu, which includes fish tacos with tangy chipotle-yogurt crema, crunchy & flavorful falafel sandwiches, chicken parmigiana sliders with homemade tomato sauce and provolone...and these are only a few of their incredibly tasty dishes. You can often find this cool team serving at Clinton Crossing Premium Outlets, but if you need catering for an upcoming event, this truck will happily make its way straight to you.
name: Food Extrovert
